     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "YoungElements[content] returns a list of elements in the Young subgroup \
with content of the symmetric group of degree n := Total[content]. \
YoungElements[content, {k1, k2, ...}] returns the elements number k1, k2, ... \
in the Young subgroup. YoungElements[n] and YoungElements[n, {k1, k2, ...}] \
are aliases of GroupElements[SymmetricGroup[n]] and \
GroupElements[SymmetricGroup[n], {k1, k2, ...}], respectively.", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "YoungElements", 
